<node id="3:22-cv-01342-JZ">
  <data key="d0">3:22-cv-01342-JZ</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">3:22-cv-01342-JZ is the unique and official federal court case number assigned to a specific legal proceeding and lawsuit between American Colloid Company and Fire Star Energy Resources LLC. This identifier serves as the primary reference for the litigation, distinguishing the matter within the judicial system and ensuring the organized tracking of all related procedural actions and documentation.

The case was officially filed in court on January 11, 2024. As the specific legal case number for this matter, 3:22-cv-01342-JZ is used to identify all legal documents, transcripts, and records associated with the dispute. This includes the recording of deposition testimony and the filing of various exhibits that constitute the evidentiary record of the proceedings. 

Throughout the legal process, 3:22-cv-01342-JZ functions as the definitive identifier for the litigation between American Colloid Company and Fire Star Energy Resources LLC. It is the designated reference point for the legal matter represented in transcripts and other formal filings submitted to the court, providing context and clarity for all testimony and records generated during the case.</data>
