<node id="Testimony">
  <data key="d0">Testimony</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The formal evidence and statements provided by witnesses during the legal proceeding, as documented in the transcript.&lt;SEP&gt;Testimony refers to the sworn witness statements recorded and indexed within the legal transcript.&lt;SEP&gt;Testimony refers to the evidence or statements provided and recorded within the legal transcript.&lt;SEP&gt;Testimony refers to the oral or written evidence given by witnesses under oath, which is a primary subject of the legal transcript.&lt;SEP&gt;Testimony consists of the sworn oral evidence or statements provided by witnesses during the legal proceeding and recorded in the transcript.&lt;SEP&gt;Testimony refers to formal statements or evidence provided during the legal proceedings, indexed across multiple pages.</data>
