  <data key="d0">Exhibit 13</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Exhibit 13 is a legal document containing an email from Michael Wagner regarding coal procurement and non-owner connections.&lt;SEP&gt;A legal exhibit consisting of emails dated February 15, 22, and 23, 2022.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 13 is a legal document containing an email string from July 27-29, 2022, between Rathke, Mr. Hauser, and others.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 13 is an email from Ms. Perkins to Mr. Jones dated May 13, 2021, corresponding with purchase order dash seven and deliveries between April 27 and May 13, 2021.</data>
