  <data key="d0">Doc #: 71-1</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Doc #: 71-1 serves as a specific document identification and reference number for a legal filing within the judicial proceedings of Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ. As a formal legal document, it was officially submitted and filed into the court record on January 11, 2024. This identifier is used to track and locate the specific filing within the court's electronic record system, ensuring it is properly indexed within the overall legal case records.

In the context of the case's documentation, Doc #: 71-1 is specifically associated with a legal transcript. It functions as a precise filing identification number that ensures the document is correctly categorized and retrievable as part of the official court record. The designation provides a unique reference for the legal materials submitted on that date, maintaining the integrity and organizational structure of the case's chronological and procedural history.</data>
