<node id="Mr. Wentz">
  <data key="d0">Mr. Wentz</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">A manager based in Bethlehem, Pennsylvania, who supervised Michael Wagner and previously managed electric contracts.&lt;SEP&gt;Mr. Wentz is an individual who provided information regarding coal specifications and identified various plant locations within the ACC system.&lt;SEP&gt;A person mentioned in the transcript who identified several industrial plants that utilize coal for their operations.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual who had a contentious phone call with Dwayne in 2021 regarding unpaid invoices.&lt;SEP&gt;Mr. Wentz is an individual who provided testimony regarding the delivery of 271 tons of coal to the Belvidere plant.&lt;SEP&gt;Mr. Wentz is the witness providing testimony in a legal deposition regarding business operations and contractual disputes with Fire Star.&lt;SEP&gt;The witness providing testimony based on his knowledge of plant operations and coal requirements.</data>
