<node id="Belvidere">
  <data key="d0">Belvidere</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Belvidere, also referred to as Bellevue in certain contexts, is an industrial plant location that serves as a key facility within the ACC network. As a primary consumer of coal, the facility relies on the material extensively for its daily operations and functions as a major destination for coal shipments. Its operational status and material needs are frequently documented in production records, stockpile data charts, and various reports regarding coal status.

The facility is a central point in a complex supply chain, receiving coal deliveries via truck transport. Its coal requirements are managed through several logistical partners and intermediaries. Notably, Fire Star has provided direct coal deliveries to the site to meet specific requirements. Additionally, the Archbold plant plays a significant role in Belvidere's logistics, often managing its coal needs and providing ground coal shipments. This relationship is particularly vital when Belvidere encounters unforeseen issues or lacks the internal capacity to grind its own material, at which point Archbold provides essential coal grinding services and material coverage.

In terms of safety and regulatory compliance, Belvidere implemented a significant combustible dust safety project to align with industry standards. This initiative, supported by Archbold, focused on managing risks associated with the handling of combustible materials. Records from 2022 indicate that the plant continued to receive coal supplies while managing these safety upgrades, utilizing planned spot buys to supplement its ongoing operational needs. Beyond its physical operations, Belvidere is frequently referenced in legal and administrative contexts, including billing discussions and transcript indices, appearing on pages 11, 20, 25, and 159. These references suggest the facility’s involvement in broader organizational or contractual activities within its industry.&lt;SEP&gt;Belvidere is a location associated with coal in the transcript header.&lt;SEP&gt;Belvidere is a location referenced multiple times in the keyword index of the legal document.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b14692172e18d355177e1f52adca6616&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72864d43546b0fdb0889bb6341c0c099&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-239b957363afa06896c850b0b3096cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00c571593b1228b7b76059ab51abd6c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-106b16a32678dd2303338174088c2dfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbd2c15dff71dc080694d39bcb9aee57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-254a838d380639a750a841f49783616f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70b9cac8deefceedbc58ea84d79ec7ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d6d709d0ec6b3472961b88797a09fc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e412217ddf7b2fe6ee24bebcb8abb8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-890fa85548914bc59a26974a429c4e21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a84012ee527927df3cba96bd82645063&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37bd5da834c461a6ccd2a7eb73c0210a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0fac00b24251700d101d62ba241bf375&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf5bccaff8fd537a70e39101e74dafe1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff8ea4fb9a276eb3036f6b13650d835&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-607b59165140de6bdf4da7d9031e9ef0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da6147e49813024d89dcb33795a793ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6adefb374fbc3e338d882ed5ad5f8b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76b142c69bd1fd0042f02d144521dea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce0536f5d7fd6c2825c2025e7a85ff94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb236f4aace79abea8a1909ae5caaed8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b265eecbe7a5b0e28f5a49767bab851</data>
