<node id="Troy">
  <data key="d0">Troy</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Troy is an industrial facility and power plant located in Indiana that operates as part of the ACC network. Primarily utilized for manufacturing and power generation processes that require coal, the facility is equipped with its own coal-grinding capabilities but frequently relies on supplemental ground coal supplies from the Archbold plant. Troy is identified as a primary destination for coal products within the network's logistics, at one point accounting for approximately half of the 2,391 tons of coal documented in specific transportation records. The facility's operational requirements are a significant factor in managing the coal supply chain and determining the tonnage requirements for the Archbold plant.

The operational status of Troy is considered a critical element in meeting regional tonnage requirements and mitigating supply disruptions. In 2022, the facility experienced a period of downtime; however, it continued to receive processed coal from Archbold during this time to maintain stockpiles and prepare for restoration. The plant’s coal usage was also a key component in calculating ACC’s total demand in June 2022. Regarding facility maintenance and safety, Troy successfully completed a combustible dust safety project in the year preceding a similar project at the York plant.

Additionally, the name Troy refers to an individual documented extensively within transportation and logistics records. This person is frequently cited throughout transcript indices, appearing in numerous sections between pages 11 and 162. In this context, Troy is primarily associated with the management and recording of tonnage and transportation data related to coal logistics.&lt;SEP&gt;Troy is a plant location mentioned by Mr. Miller as requiring a supply of ground coal.&lt;SEP&gt;Troy is an individual referenced in the possessive form "troy's" on page 139 of the transcript.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-403ed40c42348b7b34224f1b1a683c41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72864d43546b0fdb0889bb6341c0c099&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00c571593b1228b7b76059ab51abd6c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1acc0c2748bf5b184c2f1284638c9089&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-106b16a32678dd2303338174088c2dfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3cf9a12f8ab261dacc4fe581a64518c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbd2c15dff71dc080694d39bcb9aee57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-254a838d380639a750a841f49783616f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d6d709d0ec6b3472961b88797a09fc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e412217ddf7b2fe6ee24bebcb8abb8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-890fa85548914bc59a26974a429c4e21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a84012ee527927df3cba96bd82645063&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cbe08b4b2ee1e84ea1256f73eac8634&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0fac00b24251700d101d62ba241bf375&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf5bccaff8fd537a70e39101e74dafe1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d6d55a1b3a1206b911d641bfa5aaf53&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f49b6e55a9d910a0c8b04633372d3d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-700f1b36f8f5411cabae20cb2768b72c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2dfc059d1a17532d17670f1ce88581b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-170a31cc79e961c5f09937e57d832509&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76b142c69bd1fd0042f02d144521dea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce0536f5d7fd6c2825c2025e7a85ff94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb0eace2fcf56729bdb7264e72e77350&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c49f929503157c8fd745523af065f8b</data>
