<node id="Spot Buy">
  <data key="d0">Spot Buy</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A spot buy is a one-off purchase of coal made outside of a standard contract, which was attempted for the Belvidere plant.&lt;SEP&gt;A Spot Buy is a method of purchasing coal on the immediate market at current prices rather than through established contract terms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b14692172e18d355177e1f52adca6616</data>
