</node>
<node id="271 Tons">
  <data key="d0">271 Tons</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">271 tons is the specific amount of coal that was reportedly delivered directly from Fire Star to the Belvidere plant.&lt;SEP&gt;271 Tons is the specific quantity of coal that was transported to Belvidere during the period from February to April.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da6147e49813024d89dcb33795a793ca</data>
