<node id="Truck">
  <data key="d0">Truck</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Truck is identified as the primary vehicle used for transport and logistics within the documented legal proceedings and facility operations. These vehicles serve as the essential method for the movement of goods, specifically facilitating the delivery of coal to the Archbold plant. Each truckload typically carries approximately 25 tons of material. The use of trucks provides significant logistics flexibility, which allows for more fluid procurement requirements during operations.

In a specific operational context, the Truck is described as equipment owned or operated by Dwayne Cotton. This vehicle is located at the facility and is utilized to transport coal on behalf of Fire Star. The transport and delivery of coal are central to its function, with particular emphasis placed on its role in hauling processed coal. 

The importance of these vehicles is further highlighted by the operational needs of individuals such as Mr. Miller, who identified a requirement for an additional truck to manage high processing volumes. Because of their central role in the activities discussed throughout the transcript, trucks are indexed multiple times and remain a focal point of the legal and logistical documentation.&lt;SEP&gt;A vehicle owned by Dwayne Couch and utilized by Fire Star to deliver coal to customers like ACC.&lt;SEP&gt;A vehicle mentioned extensively in the transcript across numerous pages, often in contexts related to transportation and tonnage.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3aa6b92318a7dbc503df2e6bc0457f59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-403ed40c42348b7b34224f1b1a683c41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-106b16a32678dd2303338174088c2dfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-700f1b36f8f5411cabae20cb2768b72c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0fdeef1a7af602b992743ca983179b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eddfd3b5802e5b17a579266c288d6819&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-337e29c32ea2f9b0dae478beb6863a2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ef0c79c1bd88cf6c1d5c756c2cc6afc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb0eace2fcf56729bdb7264e72e77350&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8dd241e90f567b9014818ab2af2d327</data>
