<node id="Contract">
  <data key="d0">Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Contract is a formal, legally binding agreement between ACC and Fire Star (also referred to as Fire Star Energy) that governs a two-year business relationship spanning 2021 and 2022. Serving as the primary subject of litigation, this agreement provides the legal framework for the supply of coal and is the foundational document for the claims discussed throughout the court proceedings. The Contract is explicitly distinguished from informal or proposed spot buys and operates independently of ACC's internal Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) system. Due to its central role in the dispute, it is extensively indexed with numerous page and line references across the court transcript.

The agreement specifies the technical requirements and delivery terms for coal shipments, with a particular focus on the obligations to supply the Archbold facility. It details comprehensive coal supply requirements, delivery schedules, and technical specifications, including specific sulfur limits that must be maintained. Furthermore, the Contract outlines the billing practices between the parties, incorporating provisions for fuel surcharges and payment terms. 

In addition to supply and payment logistics, the Contract contains specific performance and notification clauses that define the operational relationship between ACC and Fire Star. These clauses establish the formal standards for the Deponent's company's obligations and govern how the parties must communicate regarding the execution of the agreement. As the central legal subject of the case, the Contract’s provisions regarding performance, technical adherence, and financial arrangements form the basis of the legal testimony and indexed discussions within the record.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f84d5551c37eb2124ad1961273595bcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e72cc062bf3ae931d08a4ef4fd2d0a6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d48c5c1bbcd6298267776e3258e47f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa96ecbf448943278b52e872cc3984a4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b265eecbe7a5b0e28f5a49767bab851&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4793e8c6e7ff554a30b19175bfd638a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b109525e1396d3c343edaca4b1355b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62b1979b82b13aa473c9984e5d068597&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d51b6e760a730f18b43bfd8a8366573&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eabc48583c856796f9f0b6feb5346678&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e79afae0aac4830dafd214229ec3b4cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d9e103df6e64a7c9f08b2fe14a11ac4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41190078a5f4d481949901834984dc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ec0e13bfa738407f5dd573fc3c7550c</data>
