<node id="Email">
  <data key="d0">Email</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Email refers to electronic correspondence and communications that serve as a formal written medium for business operations and legal documentation. Within the context of legal proceedings, Email is frequently cited as a source of information or evidence introduced into the record and archived within discovery indices. These documents are used to record specific attempts to procure materials, address supply chain issues at various plants, and ensure consistency in delivery schedules.

In the operational context of Fire Star, Email is utilized as a primary communication method to document delivered loads and specific logistical requirements. It is used by personnel, such as Rachel Perkins, to coordinate plant needs and maintain formal records of business transactions. For example, the medium was used to communicate with individuals named Tim and Dwayne regarding a forecasted order of 2,391 tons of coal. While it serves as a standard tool for documenting business requirements, the frequency of use can vary, as some individuals involved in the matter report using it only occasionally.&lt;SEP&gt;Email is a form of electronic correspondence referenced as evidence or documentation within the legal transcript.&lt;SEP&gt;The electronic communication medium used by Rachel Perkins and the Witness to exchange shipment and weight information.&lt;SEP&gt;The written communication sent by the Fire Star Representative to Mike Wagner to document their verbal agreement and provide follow-up discussion.&lt;SEP&gt;Email refers to a category of electronic communication referenced extensively as evidence or subject matter across numerous pages of the legal transcript.&lt;SEP&gt;Email refers to electronic communications, including specific messages and the act of emailing, which are documented as part of the case record.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa66b57078d2cf7712dd3f3924568ac6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-301a650391975642e854ed02135a0812&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c946e33e17040f1d499dc271e06eb652&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf5bccaff8fd537a70e39101e74dafe1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e2db0657fae612abbb5778b4065cd86&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0867a733c08a7b40fceaca6c36f02528&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e9f4d391d8e15587e7605c40c26d0a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4235e24e84f1af4000552965c66aa831&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b07c44e2ebc50b3456fe7fdf7de2bdbc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d35bd39a02d2b483da7cfa20826b8d6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8795514c6d030aaa61a5baf6a43cdd2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41879e062c3be5c70a69159a6ce804a</data>
