<node id="Neil">
  <data key="d0">Neil</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Neil, also referred to as Mr. Miller, is a logistics and procurement professional associated with ACC, where he serves as a primary contact for managing coal orders and plant requirements. His central responsibilities involve the coordination of coal supplies, managing volume requirements, and overseeing the processing and logistics of shipments. He is particularly noted for his role in facilitating coal deliveries to the Belvidere plant, which often involves arranging for shipments to be diverted to that specific location to meet operational needs. In his professional capacity, Neil manages complex relationships with suppliers and carriers, utilizing email as a primary tool for communicating logistical details and load requirements to truckers or individuals such as Duane Jones.

Beyond logistics, Neil serves as a key liaison and negotiator within the coal supply chain. He leverages personal connections at Fire Star to facilitate procurement and has acted as a representative of the counterparty to whom Fire Star directed complaints regarding perpetual service delays. His role includes managing sensitive communications; while he was originally responsible for informing Duane Jones about load acceptance, he was later instructed to cease communication with that party. Additionally, Neil has been involved in quality control and financial discussions, reportedly admitting to Duane Jones that ACC had made an error in its product testing and representing a party in discussions concerning payment arrears and the potential requirement for a letter of credit.

Neil is heavily documented in legal proceedings, appearing extensively in transcript indexes, which suggests a significant role or the provision of testimony in legal cases involving organizational disputes and coal supply logistics. Despite his prominence in these records, some witnesses, such as Tim, have noted that they do not communicate with him frequently. In one instance during testimony, a witness mentioned Neil's name before correcting it to Mike Wagner, though his overall involvement in negotiations and operational oversight remains a matter of record. Throughout his work, Neil has expressed professional concerns regarding inventory levels and the sufficiency of coal deliveries to ensure plant stability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3aa6b92318a7dbc503df2e6bc0457f59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-761ea9ca064011031c6c5ee686597fb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf5bccaff8fd537a70e39101e74dafe1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42181ffd60d3e3b5bf175afa8698a9f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-607b59165140de6bdf4da7d9031e9ef0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da6147e49813024d89dcb33795a793ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51f8a4880c779327848a6447b6a9410b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1fd3fce386757ff2dd2e407b6ede56de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e9f4d391d8e15587e7605c40c26d0a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbc582f48d3848d215a41b5506d1fc3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86a95d51dddd23e0ac5523de3f3ee00f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d51b6e760a730f18b43bfd8a8366573&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70464475fce6ebfbef39a68f9d9e6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-883a650c59e4458dc68f11e575383ce9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e68327bd8bee93286c96d0604c805de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-428d5f444613568ed50ee1bda1193ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba550b2e9c65dbdbc81c7c242e394da3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41879e062c3be5c70a69159a6ce804a</data>
