<node id="Carrier">
  <data key="d0">Carrier</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A Carrier refers to the entity or truck drivers responsible for the logistical transport of coal from the supplier to the destination.&lt;SEP&gt;Carrier refers to a logistics or transportation company mentioned in the context of the case.&lt;SEP&gt;The carrier is the logistics entity through which informal telephone conversations and business coordination took place.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3aa6b92318a7dbc503df2e6bc0457f59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-347bbf3851da6c1ab1118dc76a514194&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cbe08b4b2ee1e84ea1256f73eac8634</data>
