<node id="Archbold">
  <data key="d0">Archbold</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Archbold refers to a multifaceted entity encompassing a geographic location, a central industrial facility, and a distinct individual identified within legal proceedings. Geographically, Archbold is a town in Ohio located approximately one hour west of Toledo. It serves as the site for a major manufacturing and coal-processing plant operated by ACC. This facility is managed by a deponent, with Rachel Perkins serving as the administrator. The Archbold plant functions as a critical hub in an industrial network, housing the largest mill in the system and processing approximately 35 tons of coal daily to meet its internal requirements.

In its industrial and logistical capacity, the Archbold facility is responsible for grinding coal into a fine powder for both its own products and for distribution to other sites. It acts as a "gap filler" and contingent supplier for various plants, including Troy and Belvidere, and serves as the exclusive supplier for the Albion plant. The site is a significant transit point where coal—primarily sourced from Fire Star and delivered via truck—is unloaded, weighed, processed, and reloaded for further shipment. Historically, it played a vital role in the delivery routes for the Belvidere facility, although quality issues with coal shipments from Alliance occasionally impacted Archbold's ability to maintain this supply.

From a business and legal perspective, Archbold is an entity synonymous with or part of the ACC business structure and is involved in complex supply requirements and contract negotiations. The organization historically maintained a requirements contract with Fire Star, characterized by years of informal communication regarding supply needs, but it currently procures coal via the spot market. Archbold’s coal tonnage requirements, inventory levels, variable consumption patterns, and distribution logistics have been central subjects in legal depositions and business reports. These documents highlight an uptick in material requirements as the facility took on broader responsibilities to cover the needs of multiple other operations within the system.

In addition to the geographic and industrial references, Archbold is the name of a specific individual mentioned extensively in legal transcripts. This person is distinct from the town and the manufacturing plant but is heavily featured in the index of the proceedings. The individual is cited on numerous pages, including 14, 15, 17, 22, 27, 28, 29, 30, and various others up to page 173. The frequent appearance of this individual’s name across the transcript suggests a high level of involvement or significance in the legal and business matters being discussed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3aa6b92318a7dbc503df2e6bc0457f59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b14692172e18d355177e1f52adca6616&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72864d43546b0fdb0889bb6341c0c099&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-239b957363afa06896c850b0b3096cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20985475deeff0feffae4d18b011ee8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00c571593b1228b7b76059ab51abd6c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1acc0c2748bf5b184c2f1284638c9089&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-106b16a32678dd2303338174088c2dfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbd2c15dff71dc080694d39bcb9aee57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70b9cac8deefceedbc58ea84d79ec7ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b286e33aaae00d921dabd7557311e090&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-890fa85548914bc59a26974a429c4e21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a84012ee527927df3cba96bd82645063&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37bd5da834c461a6ccd2a7eb73c0210a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0fac00b24251700d101d62ba241bf375&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f49b6e55a9d910a0c8b04633372d3d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff8ea4fb9a276eb3036f6b13650d835&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a2fa8d820719e1257925db86c0ebc64b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-607b59165140de6bdf4da7d9031e9ef0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51f8a4880c779327848a6447b6a9410b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-170a31cc79e961c5f09937e57d832509&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6651d4b1167389e3589940fb1cba165&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8fa155c99076902d5c68d436af59b4c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c1a43f78b5ed9fc7d6bf6a28877a7eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76b142c69bd1fd0042f02d144521dea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce0536f5d7fd6c2825c2025e7a85ff94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eddfd3b5802e5b17a579266c288d6819&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89fa75b320a462be370f07eb405c8186&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d265c5065bea7006d9e21d1c75d8eb5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2e3168e22d9c7a7d9e58835f3e33743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4793e8c6e7ff554a30b19175bfd638a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-86a95d51dddd23e0ac5523de3f3ee00f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9ab40d430700b4968945f064e8400cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872baedd657194f10bff17517ac33313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58baed9d52d175a1f6d13d75ff252edc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d51b6e760a730f18b43bfd8a8366573&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea0c3d9ff35641a8bb5a123cadebd49d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d41d933f94ead56d3ee9ccb33dd28b07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-548158467ea27bbcbd50237943afe1b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8dd241e90f567b90