<node id="Aric Wentz">
  <data key="d0">Aric Wentz</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Aric Wentz is an employee of the American Colloid Company (ACC) who has played a central role in managing business relationships and legal matters for the firm. In his professional capacity at ACC, Wentz has interacted with several stakeholders, including holding professional conversations with the Respondent and managing communications with Fire Star. Notably, he took on a demanding role in managing the relationship between ACC and Fire Star following a dispute regarding sulfur readings. During this period, he served as the point of contact for complaints from Fire Star concerning operational delays and payment issues.

In the context of legal proceedings, Aric Wentz served as a witness, providing testimony under oath during a video-recorded deposition. His testimony primarily focused on coal requirements and related operations. His involvement is further documented through various forms of communication, including phone conversations and electronic correspondence. Wentz was involved in email exchanges documented in Exhibit 85 and was the recipient of an email sent by a witness regarding coal operations.

Additionally, Aric Wentz authored a formal letter dated April 12, 2021, addressed to a witness involved in the case. His multi-faceted involvement—ranging from operational management and dispute resolution to providing sworn legal testimony—highlights his significant position in the interactions between the American Colloid Company and its associates, particularly concerning coal operations and the contractual disputes arising with Fire Star.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b14692172e18d355177e1f52adca6616&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82750d61ecd8735fd405d620ba554887&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-170a31cc79e961c5f09937e57d832509&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6513ff10fc090a173beec2a8235adc3d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4fdf13248aed5385075305f0203ad2b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbc582f48d3848d215a41b5506d1fc3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d51b6e760a730f18b43bfd8a8366573&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70464475fce6ebfbef39a68f9d9e6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47a4c64d17422cabf37987557b8d9c98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29e3634a63146460c270b610b9966f0c</data>
