<node id="Tim Jones">
  <data key="d0">Tim Jones</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Tim Jones is an individual associated with the company Fire Star, where he plays a significant role in managing logistics and financial communications. He is frequently identified alongside another individual named Dwayne as part of a group referred to as "the Joneses." Within his capacity at Fire Star, Tim Jones is responsible for receiving communications regarding coal delivery quantities and purchase orders. In the early part of 2022, he was specifically noted for identifying an invoice exception issue and was involved in correspondence regarding the necessity for payments between March and June 2022.

The professional activities of Tim Jones are documented in various records, including an email exchange regarding deliveries and requirements found in Exhibit 11. He was also a recipient of internal emails concerning coal processing activities related to Archbold. His communications, including text messages, are preserved as part of Exhibit 8. 

Tim Jones’s knowledge and permission are considered central to investigations involving coal shipments, though his level of awareness has been a subject of scrutiny. Despite his role in delivery logistics, he was notably not informed of the decision to redirect coal shipments to the Belvidere plant. His awareness of certain other coal shipments has been questioned, and during deposition testimony, his understanding of specific business connections remained unclear. Consequently, he is characterized as a key figure whose involvement and oversight are critical to understanding the operational and investigative context of the shipments in question.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual mentioned as a recipient or subject of letters in the exhibit index.&lt;SEP&gt;Tim Jones is an individual involved in the legal proceedings and recipient of correspondence documented in Exhibit 10.&lt;SEP&gt;Tim Jones is the recipient of a letter from Ms. Rathke dated July 20, 2022, identified as Exhibit 11.&lt;SEP&gt;Tim Jones is an individual associated with Fire Star who occasionally interacts with B&amp;W regarding coal.</data>
