<node id="The Joneses">
  <data key="d0">The Joneses</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Joneses refers to Dwayne Jones and his associates who are connected to Fire Star and coal processing operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Individuals mentioned in relation to their knowledge of direct coal shipments from Fire Star to Belvidere.&lt;SEP&gt;The Joneses refers to the collective authority of Dwayne and Tim over coal operations, permissions, and logistics.&lt;SEP&gt;The Joneses are a group of individuals associated with Fire Star who were involved in payment disputes with the deponent.&lt;SEP&gt;A group or family associated with Fire Star to whom information regarding coal requirements was potentially communicated.&lt;SEP&gt;A collective reference to Tim and Dwayne Jones, who were not informed about the redirection of coal shipments.&lt;SEP&gt;The Joneses are the principals or owners of Fire Star whose knowledge of coal shipment arrangements was a subject of inquiry.</data>
