<node id="Tim">
  <data key="d0">Tim</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Tim is a co-owner of Fire Star Energy Resources LLC and the brother of Dwayne Jones (also referred to as Duane), who is identified as the Respondent or Deponent in related legal proceedings. Within the organizational structure of Fire Star, Tim holds a central role managing administrative and financial operations. His primary responsibilities include handling the company’s financial aspects, billing, invoicing, and paperwork, as well as maintaining financial records and tracking overall profits. He is specifically noted for his involvement in processing weight data and receiving invoices essential to the company's coal operations.

In his operational capacity, Tim is responsible for monitoring the official company email address, FireStarEnergy@Hotmail.com. He serves as a primary recipient for critical business communications, including emails regarding significant coal orders, specific tonnage requirements, and reports detailing persistent coal supply shortages. Tim is tasked with reporting these shortages and coordinating with other personnel to resolve payment-related issues. His professional interactions include receiving billing communications from Rachel Perkins and correspondence from Mr. Miller concerning future coal supply requirements.

Tim’s involvement is extensively documented in a legal context, where he is frequently mentioned throughout the index of a legal transcript, specifically appearing on pages 8, 49, and 169. He provided testimony as a witness during a deposition, answering questions regarding Fire Star’s invoicing, weight data, and professional interactions. While some individuals involved in the case reported having no direct business dealings with him, Tim was identified as a recipient of communications regarding legal complaints and was involved in organizational responses to payment disputes. Although his name was initially raised regarding a matter of authorization or permission, a subsequent correction identified his brother, Dwayne, as the relevant party for that specific instance. He is also noted for his specific knowledge regarding relevant dates and the receipt of correspondence from B&amp;W Resources, Inc.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3aa6b92318a7dbc503df2e6bc0457f59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-403ed40c42348b7b34224f1b1a683c41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72864d43546b0fdb0889bb6341c0c099&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-239b957363afa06896c850b0b3096cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5615da5f26bf1a4c451ff93c5d9cf990&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20985475deeff0feffae4d18b011ee8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa66b57078d2cf7712dd3f3924568ac6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea56e06fa48990cb993a7e9f44e99a73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3cf9a12f8ab261dacc4fe581a64518c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad7ed4f7be4010bb04a8fb57444930ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91ae622aa3716a4b71176bab6a4c634c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d718117f6b8f471655c35924d8691d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b506a28447e4a2e3d78916201636374&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc4469d9a1123a581838f093850a0ec4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4fdf13248aed5385075305f0203ad2b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-337e29c32ea2f9b0dae478beb6863a2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c897eacbc52ea3409f410ddbf1dd519&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e9f4d391d8e15587e7605c40c26d0a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a43620a63dc78a8a9bfac32a9b5945ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ec881e55ad83fdc9af56880be9399bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d9349135c3baf847b28d5827d84e441&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff1b2e3ad64f8ef5a6f5ccbddd86effc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e61818cb941a92071ee2c7a3e3a8fb23&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b87aa2374a79dfe9801180e61a932d0c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d51b6e760a730f18b43bfd8a8366573&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2028cbb4e322060dc3699f091af3659&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf3b2577bfe15593df5908753840d030&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0ed161cb265564fc00297c21536c2dbb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c49f929503157c8fd745523af065f8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fff22f122484c9f576c6d89686abf9f0</data>
