<node id="Exhibit 3">
  <data key="d0">Exhibit 3</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Exhibit 3 is a specific document or email record presented as evidence during the legal proceeding.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 3 is a document referenced in the deposition, identified as being related to the March 8, 2022, communication.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 3 is a legal document or excerpt referenced during the questioning regarding tonnage and demand.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 3 is an Excel chart produced under Bates 594 that tracks coal deliveries, invoice amounts, and payment dates for transactions with Fire Star.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 3 is an email from Mike Wagner to Fire Star that is included as part of the legal complaint.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 3 is a Fire Star invoice pertaining to the purchase order identified in Exhibit 1.`&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 3 is an invoice from Fire Star that is dated January 4.</data>
