  <data key="d0">Personally Identifiable Information</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Sensitive personal data that is protected under the Gramm-Leach-Bliley Act and managed securely by Veritext Legal Solutions.&lt;SEP&gt;Information that can be used on its own or with other information to identify, contact, or locate a single person.&lt;SEP&gt;Personally Identifiable Information (PII) refers to any data that can be used to distinguish or trace an individual's identity.&lt;SEP&gt;Personally Identifiable Information (PII) refers to data that can be used to identify a specific individual, which is protected under the Gramm-Leach-Bliley Act.&lt;SEP&gt;Personally Identifiable Information (PII) is sensitive data used to uniquely identify an individual, which Veritext Legal Solutions is committed to protecting.</data>
