  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Sensitive medical data that is subject to specific privacy regulations and protections under HIPAA.&lt;SEP&gt;Sensitive medical and health-related information that is subject to confidentiality regulations under HIPAA.&lt;SEP&gt;Protected Health Information refers to sensitive health data that is handled and protected according to HIPAA regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Protected Health Information is data regarding a person's health status or healthcare provision that is protected under HIPAA regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Protected Health Information refers to sensitive health-related data that is subject to privacy protections under HIPAA regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Protected Health Information (PHI) is any health-related data that is protected under HIPAA regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Protected Health Information refers to sensitive health-related data that is subject to confidentiality regulations under HIPAA.</data>
