  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Complaint is the formal legal document outlining the amicable history and subsequent dispute between the parties.&lt;SEP&gt;The Complaint is a legal document to which an email concerning coal tonnage requirements was attached as evidence.&lt;SEP&gt;The Complaint is a legal document mentioned in the testimony that outlines the grievances and the timeline of the business relationship between the parties.&lt;SEP&gt;A legal document outlining allegations against Fire Star, primarily focused on breaches occurring in 2022.&lt;SEP&gt;The Complaint is a legal document outlining ACC's claims against Fire Star, specifically regarding the lack of supply starting in June 2022.&lt;SEP&gt;The Complaint is a legal document containing exhibits such as Exhibit 3 and Exhibit 4.</data>
