  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">January 11, 2024, serves as the official filing date for several key legal documents within the court system for the legal proceedings identified as Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ. This date marks a recorded point for the submission of various items of legal documentation and transcripts necessary for the maintenance and progression of the case's official records. As a specific procedural milestone, it represents the point at which these legal instruments, evidentiary documents, and formal records were officially entered into and recognized by the court.

The filings recorded on January 11, 2024, include several specifically numbered documents that are central to the case history. Most notably, Document 66-1 was officially filed and recorded multiple times across the court header for this date. Other significant filings include Document 69-1 and Document 71-1, both of which are cited as established components of the case's documented history. Additionally, Document 72-1 was officially entered into the case records on this same day.

The variety of documentation submitted on January 11, 2024, encompasses a range of legal materials, including an errata sheet, a deposition document, and a document index. The records also include a legal transcript and its associated documentation. Collectively, these filings ensure that these evidentiary and formal materials are properly integrated into the legal framework of Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ.</data>
