<node id="Fire Star Energy Resources, LLC">
  <data key="d0">Fire Star Energy Resources, LLC</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Fire Star Energy Resources, LLC is a company that has been active in the coal business for approximately 15 to 16 years. The entity is currently involved in a legal dispute with the American Colloid Company, serving as the defendant and counterclaimant in Case No. 3:22-cv-01342.

Throughout this legal action, Fire Star Energy Resources, LLC is represented by counsel from the law firm Frost Brown Todd. The case represents a primary legal matter for the company, as it addresses claims brought forth by the American Colloid Company while simultaneously pursuing its own counterclaims within the same proceedings.</data>
