<node id="Sarah Rathke">
  <data key="d0">Sarah Rathke</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Sarah Rathke is a legal professional and attorney who serves as legal counsel for the plaintiff, American Colloid Company. She is a primary participant in the legal proceedings associated with Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ, where she is frequently identified in documentation by her name and her contact information, specifically the email address sarah.rathke.

In her capacity as an attorney, Sarah Rathke is responsible for examining witnesses and conducting legal inquiries. Her work includes the cross-examination of Dwayne Jones and questioning during depositions that cover topics such as coal procurement, logistics, and pricing. Her involvement is extensively documented throughout the legal transcripts, with numerous references to her presence and specific testimony pages noted in the case indices.</data>
