<node id="Exhibit 8">
  <data key="d0">Exhibit 8</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Exhibit 8 consists of text messages produced during discovery that are used as evidence during the questioning of the Witness.&lt;SEP&gt;A set of text messages produced in discovery, referenced during the deposition as containing communications from June.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 8 is a legal document containing text messages between Dwayne and ACC representatives, used for identification in a legal case.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 8 is a document previously referenced in the legal proceedings before Exhibit 9.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 8 is a document used during the deposition to establish the timeline of coal supply between the parties.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 8 is an email from Ms. Perkins dated March 1, 2021, detailing coal deliveries from February 12 to 24.&lt;SEP&gt;Exhibit 8 is an email from Ms. Perkins dated March 1, 2021, reflecting 611.01 tons of coal corresponding with purchase order dash four.</data>
