<node id="The Plant">
  <data key="d0">The Plant</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Plant is a facility where materials are stored, ground, and managed, typically holding about 1,000 tons of inventory in rotation.&lt;SEP&gt;The Plant is the industrial facility operated by ACC where material deliveries are received and managed.&lt;SEP&gt;The industrial facility operated by ACC that maintained a positive working relationship with Fire Star until 2022.&lt;SEP&gt;The Plant is the industrial facility associated with ACC where employees like Neil Miller and Steve were stationed and where coal was delivered.&lt;SEP&gt;The facility or entity described as having a policy of releasing weights slowly to buy more time.</data>
