  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">June 2022 is the month when a defect was identified in the storage silo at the Troy plant, leading to operational safety issues.&lt;SEP&gt;The specific time period marking the total cessation of coal deliveries from Fire Star to ACC.&lt;SEP&gt;The time period during which text message communications regarding payments and shipping occurred between Dwayne and Mr. Miller.</data>
