<node id="Mike Wagner">
  <data key="d0">Mike Wagner</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Mike Wagner is a former employee of ACC who served as a primary point of contact for coal orders, information, and logistics starting in early 2021. Based near Houston, Texas, Wagner remained with the company until his resignation in September 2022. Throughout his tenure, he was the designated representative through whom Fire Star and its personnel, including Duane Jones, were instructed to route communications. He specifically took over the responsibility of coordinating coal deliveries with Jones after another individual, Neil, was directed to cease communication.

In his operational role, Mike Wagner determined coal delivery quantities and managed inquiries regarding coal prices, haul rates for Archbold, and the feasibility of shipping to various plants. He was actively involved in discussions regarding fuel surcharges and contract modifications, often requesting written confirmation for these changes via email. Wagner's responsibilities also included managing shipment weight data and responding to requests for more prompt reporting. On March 15, 2021, he visited Fire Star's facilities in person to address specific product quality issues.

Mike Wagner functioned as a key communicator for ACC, drafting official letters and emails to Fire Star while consulting with legal counsel regarding their content. His correspondence, which often referred to his colleagues as "the team," covered a range of topics including resolved invoices and shipping schedules. He was also a central figure in managing internal and external disputes, having authored emails expressing frustration over contract violations and internal payment processing delays. Consequently, he was the individual to whom Fire Star directed complaints regarding late weight data and payment tactics, and he was the representative verbally informed by witnesses that ACC was in default of its agreements.

Furthermore, Mike Wagner was involved in discussions regarding the availability of business opportunities and the right of first refusal for 2023 business, though he reportedly did not respond to a June telephone inquiry on the latter. He also served as a source of information for Mr. Jones regarding the actions and attitude of Aric Wentz. Within the context of legal and business record-keeping, Wagner's communications via text and email have been subjects of search. While he maintained frequent contact with external parties, some associates noted that they spoke with him regularly but never met him in person.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5e21ed3795086662478d7a51f321f88e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d6d55a1b3a1206b911d641bfa5aaf53&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f49b6e55a9d910a0c8b04633372d3d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce0536f5d7fd6c2825c2025e7a85ff94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b68abd5df047acac26c37b8f51c0f65b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbc582f48d3848d215a41b5506d1fc3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9ab40d430700b4968945f064e8400cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872baedd657194f10bff17517ac33313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d699f913a8b37597b19cd0e1b1798b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b07c44e2ebc50b3456fe7fdf7de2bdbc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3685a8c4ea16ed81736bdfa10022fc8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58baed9d52d175a1f6d13d75ff252edc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e79afae0aac4830dafd214229ec3b4cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2028cbb4e322060dc3699f091af3659&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70464475fce6ebfbef39a68f9d9e6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-883a650c59e4458dc68f11e575383ce9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f348a463c6446420e2f4187560950349&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47a4c64d17422cabf37987557b8d9c98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2303ff741d8017a5176d75a2abdfe5ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d41d933f94ead56d3ee9ccb33dd28b07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41190078a5f4d481949901834984dc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-428d5f444613568ed50ee1bda1193ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe738ecfa2bfb6f1e43bab47e86f274a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41879e062c3be5c70a69159a6ce804a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-410e248374ac5c766b1c22f0ac604a22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-29e3634a63146460c270b610b9966f0c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2dc9b5b950d7e245002aa75cb40b381</data>
