<node id="Ms. Perkins">
  <data key="d0">Ms. Perkins</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Ms. Perkins, also referred to as Rachel, is an individual associated with ACC who plays a central role in the logistical and financial coordination between ACC and Fire Star Energy. She is primarily responsible for providing critical data regarding coal shipments, including weight measurements, delivery quantities, and purchase order information. Her communications, which are conducted via text messages and emails, serve as a foundational component of the billing and invoicing process.

Throughout her professional activities, Ms. Perkins has authored several emails that have been formally identified as legal exhibits, specifically Exhibits 8, 18, 22, 25, 36, 64, and 66. These documents contain detailed information such as shipment delivery dates, coal weights, and purchase order details. Her correspondence has been directed to various individuals, including Mr. Jones, Tim, and a person named Cotton, as well as other witnesses and deponents. These communications often address specific logistical matters, such as unmet coal requirements and the calculation of payment amounts based on delivery data.

Chronological records indicate that Ms. Perkins sent significant emails regarding coal delivery weights and purchase orders on August 13, 2021, and December 17, 2021. Additionally, it was noted that in early 2022, she was recovering from surgery, though she continued to be recognized as the individual responsible for issuing weight lists and providing logistical updates related to coal shipments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3f49b6e55a9d910a0c8b04633372d3d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e79afae0aac4830dafd214229ec3b4cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5104adfc9db5e929c6fe776c8ad944ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f348a463c6446420e2f4187560950349&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8402b590f10e3a8b65a78faf2a1ad55c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d9e103df6e64a7c9f08b2fe14a11ac4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06bfce7cab4edf6f90244a7388e98ee9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf3b2577bfe15593df5908753840d030&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c49f929503157c8fd745523af065f8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5112ed7e479baa078942ba54c24c9817&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c04f49f2f1828e187e2d46075aba09f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe738ecfa2bfb6f1e43bab47e86f274a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba550b2e9c65dbdbc81c7c242e394da3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c29dc02ae5ef2a8f3e0d50f1a1f7504&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30d0b22d79b47320c1f6cc47e1d3a998&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e5e24529707d149e3a4818e96dcbae7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3768689425a6da71a09b43a110e4c9b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fff22f122484c9f576c6d89686abf9f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21b64866580445e8fae3d73e6cbdeafa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15afec084e7d4db2b6330ebd480bab32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2dc9b5b950d7e245002aa75cb40b381&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f43f20395a640ee603064daae404e1d</data>
