<node id="Belvidere Plant">
  <data key="d0">Belvidere Plant</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Belvidere Plant is an industrial manufacturing facility located in Illinois that specializes in the production of foundry casting products. As a significant component of a broader supply system, the facility utilizes industrial materials and processes similar to those employed at the Albion and Archbold plants. Its operations rely heavily on coal, with specific requirements regarding moisture content and size specifications that fluctuate based on the capacity of the plant's equipment.

The facility maintains a functional relationship with the Archbold plant, often sharing coal with similar attributes. The Belvidere Plant relies on the Archbold facility for grinding services when the quality of the available coal supply is low. Additionally, the Belvidere Plant serves as a destination for coal shipments diverted from the Archbold plant when that facility encounters its own processing limitations.

Logistically, the Belvidere Plant has been a recipient of significant coal deliveries, including a shipment of approximately 271 to 272 tons from Fire Star between February and April of the previous year. These deliveries were part of a supply chain in which Fire Star was allegedly unaware that the Belvidere Plant was the final destination for the materials provided. The plant continues to function as a key destination for coal supplies, particularly when other facilities in the network are unable to process incoming shipments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42181ffd60d3e3b5bf175afa8698a9f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a806f0397efbdda46f27050ca5f69a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51f8a4880c779327848a6447b6a9410b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2dfc059d1a17532d17670f1ce88581b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9233f58a4f0f40156583723a1ef120cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8fa155c99076902d5c68d436af59b4c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65ca06b1229dac02f972ebae8fde3f98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1db5458af1cededb9c5054e17294a8c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3802f42ea2e90df66cc37eb93f82943&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff296c565c3f4e80b9959ae67262e606&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0fdeef1a7af602b992743ca983179b0</data>
  <data key="d4">Deposition by Defendant -- Aric Wentz (Supervisor at Plaintiff) -- April 14, 2023, 0859.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1777296766</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
