<node id="The Deponent">
  <data key="d0">The Deponent</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Deponent is the individual providing sworn testimony in a legal proceeding and serves as a representative for Fire Star Energy. Identified as a managing member and 50% owner of the company, The Deponent is responsible for Fire Star’s finances and accounting. In addition to their corporate role, The Deponent is noted as being the sibling of an individual named Tim.

In August 2020, The Deponent assumed responsibility for the MTI supply chain and managed the contract associated with Fire Star. Their operational duties include managing business operations, overseeing coal supply logistics, and addressing matters related to fuel surcharges. Specifically, The Deponent handles coal orders from ACC and is responsible for sending invoices on behalf of Fire Star and communicating with ACC personnel.

Throughout the legal proceeding, The Deponent is questioned regarding business documents, coal transactions, and the production of evidence such as emails. They were personally involved in communications and decision-making for Fire Star regarding ACC Coal. Furthermore, The Deponent conducted searches for text communications relevant to the lawsuit and testified about the company's internal communications and various business transactions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9233f58a4f0f40156583723a1ef120cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e9f4d391d8e15587e7605c40c26d0a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a43620a63dc78a8a9bfac32a9b5945ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4793e8c6e7ff554a30b19175bfd638a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9ab40d430700b4968945f064e8400cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f348a463c6446420e2f4187560950349&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8402b590f10e3a8b65a78faf2a1ad55c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a24884e475800cf1128930e1da431ac0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41190078a5f4d481949901834984dc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15afec084e7d4db2b6330ebd480bab32</data>
  <data key="d4">Deposition by Defendant -- Aric Wentz (Supervisor at Plaintiff) -- April 14, 2023, 0859.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;Deposition by Plaintiff -- Dwayne Jones (Owner of Defendant) -- August 17, 2023, 1101.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;Deposition by Plaintiff -- Timothy Jones (Owner of Defendant) -- July 17, 2023, 0938.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1777298937</data>
