  <data key="d0">Health Insurance Portability And Accountability Act</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA) is a federal law that establishes standards for the protection of sensitive patient health information.&lt;SEP&gt;The Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA) is a federal law that establishes standards for protecting sensitive patient health information.</data>
