  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Statement Of Changes">
  <data key="d0">Statement Of Changes</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Statement of Changes is a signed document listing modifications made by the deponent to a deposition transcript along with the reasons for those changes.&lt;SEP&gt;The Statement of Changes is a document signed by a deponent that lists specific modifications to a deposition transcript and the reasons for those changes.&lt;SEP&gt;The Statement of Changes is a formal document where a deponent records any corrections or modifications to their deposition transcript.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ab822257583152b1080598f158d5ff4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6e556868aec38819b729d4931728e17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b87aa2374a79dfe9801180e61a932d0c</data>
