<node id="Weights">
  <data key="d0">Weights</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Weights refer to the precise quantitative measurements of tonnage for truck deliveries, specifically coal shipments, which are essential for the billing and invoicing process. These measurements are typically provided by ACC to Fire Star to facilitate the issuance of invoices. The data often represents destination weights from specific locations, such as the Archbold site. Within the operational workflow, these measurements determine both the specific content and the timing of the invoices, as the billing process cannot be completed until the specific data is received and processed.

The delivery of Weights is frequently documented in correspondence involving Ms. Perkins, who provides the measured quantity of coal loads via email to ensure accurate financial records. This data serves as the foundational basis for Fire Star to generate invoices, reflecting the recorded measurements of coal shipments. The records of these weights are critical components of the communication between the parties involved in managing the logistics and financial transactions of coal shipments.

In a broader context within indexed testimony, Weights also refers to various objects or measurements of mass that serve as frequent subjects of discussion. These mentions encompass both the specific shipping data used for generating invoices and general physical measurements of mass relevant to the legal proceedings and evidence recorded in the testimony.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b00f5db7b778b08602a372df17667706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbc582f48d3848d215a41b5506d1fc3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-746f3438b7d2219af5f396745296fbea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e79afae0aac4830dafd214229ec3b4cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf3b2577bfe15593df5908753840d030&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5112ed7e479baa078942ba54c24c9817&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe738ecfa2bfb6f1e43bab47e86f274a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c29dc02ae5ef2a8f3e0d50f1a1f7504&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e5e24529707d149e3a4818e96dcbae7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41879e062c3be5c70a69159a6ce804a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fff22f122484c9f576c6d89686abf9f0</data>
