<node id="Duane Jones">
  <data key="d0">Duane Jones</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Duane Jones is an individual closely associated with Fire Star Energy, serving as a 50% owner of the company and the brother of the deponent, who is also referred to as the witness or Cotton. Within the organization, Jones occupies a central operational role, managing the day-to-day activities at Fire Star's loadout facility. His responsibilities include overseeing coal shipments, managing tonnage, and coordinating the logistics of coal orders and deliveries.

Acting as the primary conduit for communication between Fire Star and B&amp;W, Duane Jones is responsible for the flow of information regarding business operations. He serves as the point of contact for requesting coal from Hazard and receives critical updates regarding the capacity for coal loads that can be accepted. Jones was specifically involved in communicating coal supply information and delivery schedules for the Archbold plant to Neil Miller, with recorded interactions regarding these shipments occurring throughout 2021.

In addition to his logistical duties, Duane Jones participates in high-level business discussions and technical coordination. He has held meetings with Mike Wagner regarding business matters and was a participant in communications where it was reported that ACC's testing was incorrect. His involvement in the company’s operations and his professional exchanges are further documented in legal records, specifically appearing in text communications identified as Exhibit 38 and Exhibit 39.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c76cedacf73005e334dc4f7459e02458&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce30e6e385c37b0067d444ae6548e003&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70464475fce6ebfbef39a68f9d9e6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-883a650c59e4458dc68f11e575383ce9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a24884e475800cf1128930e1da431ac0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8dd241e90f567b9014818ab2af2d327&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c04f49f2f1828e187e2d46075aba09f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe738ecfa2bfb6f1e43bab47e86f274a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ee88bb60d54bb9669aab0679563e07b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-320ecdd7bc0257e71d40887d3e9b4742&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41879e062c3be5c70a69159a6ce804a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-410e248374ac5c766b1c22f0ac604a22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07fe3dd18c0d678950b64b49cff4b258&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3768689425a6da71a09b43a110e4c9b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21b64866580445e8fae3d73e6cbdeafa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2dc9b5b950d7e245002aa75cb40b381</data>
