<node id="Duane">
  <data key="d0">Duane</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Duane is a central figure and deponent in legal proceedings, with his involvement documented extensively across a transcript ranging from page 11 to 169. He is identified as a witness who provided testimony on several matters, including the transition to a new invoicing procedure and his efforts to escalate concerns regarding late payments. Duane is noted to have various familial connections within the context of the proceedings, described variously as the brother of the witness Mr. Jones, the brother of Tim, and the brother of Mr. Wagner.

Within his professional capacity, Duane is associated with Fire Star, where he serves as the primary contact for customers like ACC when placing coal orders. He is responsible for handling discussions with ACC personnel and managing the logistical aspects of coal shipments. His role involved direct coordination with Michael Wagner regarding shipping schedules, particularly when Tim was on vacation, and he acted as a key source of information for others involved in these operations.

Duane acted as a significant communication link between Fire Star and its clients, specifically regarding contractual limitations and payment issues. He frequently corresponded with Neil Miller regarding coal supplies, production challenges, and future supply requirements. Records indicate that Duane informed Miller in May that ACC was significantly behind on its payments and communicated the resulting limitations of their coal supply contract. His interactions often focused on the impact of late payments and the specific shipping constraints faced by the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4235e24e84f1af4000552965c66aa831&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac3fad32fec8e4d7d33ae790368a0655&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58baed9d52d175a1f6d13d75ff252edc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d51b6e760a730f18b43bfd8a8366573&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eabc48583c856796f9f0b6feb5346678&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2028cbb4e322060dc3699f091af3659&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5a649e347db48560371ae468a01e05ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f348a463c6446420e2f4187560950349&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47a4c64d17422cabf37987557b8d9c98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2303ff741d8017a5176d75a2abdfe5ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41190078a5f4d481949901834984dc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c49f929503157c8fd745523af065f8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-428d5f444613568ed50ee1bda1193ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-182570a48865445e060a0af61ce1cd8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d35bd39a02d2b483da7cfa20826b8d6e</data>
