  <data key="d2">Doc #: 66-1 is a specific document identifier and exhibit number assigned to a legal filing within the records of federal court Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ. It serves as a unique entry within the electronic court filing system, constituting an integral part of the official legal record and evidentiary material for the ongoing proceedings.

