<edge source="ACC" target="Archbold Plant">
  <data key="d7">7.0</data>
  <data key="d8">ACC defines the coal requirements of the Archbold plant as including the volume ground for both its own products and other plants.&lt;SEP&gt;ACC operates the Archbold Plant and manages its resource requirements for production.&lt;SEP&gt;ACC operates the Archbold Plant, which receives coal shipments from Fire Star Energy Resources LLC.&lt;SEP&gt;ACC owns and operates the Archbold plant where the coal supplied by Fire Star is delivered.&lt;SEP&gt;ACC is the organization responsible for the operations at the Archbold plant.&lt;SEP&gt;The Archbold Plant is a specific facility owned or operated by ACC.&lt;SEP&gt;ACC maintains coal requirements and operations at the Archbold plant.</data>
  <data key="d9">facility,facility management,industrial facility,operational position,operational site,operations,ownership,requirement definition,resource management</data>
