<edge source="ACC" target="Mike Wagner">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between Mike Wagner and ACC is characterized by his role as a key employee and representative who served as a primary point of contact for the organization. Mike Wagner was affiliated with ACC until his voluntary resignation in September 2022. Beginning in 2021, he served as the primary contact for coordinating information and coal orders, eventually taking over responsibility for communicating with individuals such as Duane Jones regarding coal shipments.

In his professional capacity, Mike Wagner acted as the central figure through whom all delivery communications were expected to be routed. His responsibilities included representing ACC in discussions concerning order rates, surcharges, and fuel charges. He served as a representative during site visits, such as to Fire Star's facilities, and communicated frequently with vendors on behalf of the company regarding pricing and business agreements. Notably, Fire Star directed complaints to him concerning delayed weight data and payments. As a liaison, Wagner also inquired about specific shipments and handled communications claiming that certain invoices had been resolved.

Beyond logistics and vendor relations, Mike Wagner was identified as a point of contact for ACC regarding business and contractual rights. He was aware of the company’s delinquent payment status and received a formal notice of default on behalf of the organization. During discovery requests, his communications were specifically highlighted as relevant to ACC's legal and business matters. However, the company has clarified that certain comments made by Wagner regarding legal inaction were his personal opinions and did not represent the official corporate stance of ACC.</data>
  <data key="d9">affiliation,business communication,business operations,communication management,communication role,contact person,employment,point of contact,professional affiliation,professional association,professional capacity,professional contact,professional opinion,representation,representative,resignation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7d6d55a1b3a1206b911d641bfa5aaf53&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce0536f5d7fd6c2825c2025e7a85ff94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbc582f48d3848d215a41b5506d1fc3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9ab40d430700b4968945f064e8400cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872baedd657194f10bff17517ac33313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d699f913a8b37597b19cd0e1b1798b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b07c44e2ebc50b3456fe7fdf7de2bdbc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3685a8c4ea16ed81736bdfa10022fc8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58baed9d52d175a1f6d13d75ff252edc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2028cbb4e322060dc3699f091af3659&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70464475fce6ebfbef39a68f9d9e6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f348a463c6446420e2f4187560950349&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47a4c64d17422cabf37987557b8d9c98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2303ff741d8017a5176d75a2abdfe5ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-428d5f444613568ed50ee1bda1193ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41879e062c3be5c70a69159a6ce804a</data>
