<edge source="ACC" target="Neil Miller">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between ACC and Neil Miller is defined by Miller's role as a key employee and representative of the organization, specifically serving as the plant manager at the Archbold facility. In this capacity, Neil Miller is responsible for overseeing the plant's operational requirements and managing load capacities. He is an integral member of the ACC organization, acting as a primary point of contact for the facility's day-to-day business matters and supply chain logistics.

Neil Miller’s professional duties at ACC heavily involve the procurement of coal supplies. He is responsible for communicating with external vendors, such as Fire Star, to coordinate business transactions and address the plant's energy needs. While he was previously the primary individual responsible for placing coal orders, records indicate that he was eventually instructed to cease direct contact regarding these specific procurement activities.

In a legal or administrative context, Neil Miller's interactions and correspondence on behalf of ACC have been subject to scrutiny. His communications were specifically searched during a discovery process, and witnesses have been questioned regarding the nature of his messages, including whether certain communications he sent were potentially ignored by recipients. These details underscore his position as an official representative whose professional conduct and communications are closely tied to ACC’s operational and business history.</data>
  <data key="d9">Employment,affiliation,business operations,communication,employment,management,plant operations,procurement,professional affiliation,representation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7566eaf604ece2fba223c2c887c38088&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4fdf13248aed5385075305f0203ad2b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0221087bef0e7a6186d86f99a70ffc95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d699f913a8b37597b19cd0e1b1798b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58baed9d52d175a1f6d13d75ff252edc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47a4c64d17422cabf37987557b8d9c98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2303ff741d8017a5176d75a2abdfe5ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-320ecdd7bc0257e71d40887d3e9b4742&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3768689425a6da71a09b43a110e4c9b3</data>
