<edge source="JZ" target="Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ, JZ) identifies the specific judicial assignment and oversight of the legal matter designated as Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ. The initials "JZ" within the case identifier denote the presiding judge or judicial officer who is formally assigned to the matter. This individual is responsible for presiding over all legal proceedings and managing the various stages of the litigation process.

As the judicial official associated with this case, JZ holds the authority over the proceedings and the management of all related legal documents. The role involves comprehensive oversight, ensuring that the case is conducted according to established legal standards and procedures. This designation clarifies that JZ is the specific court official linked to the administrative and judicial management of the identified legal action.&lt;SEP&gt;The case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ is assigned to the judicial official identified by the initials JZ.&lt;SEP&gt;The judge identified as JZ has judicial oversight and responsibility for the proceedings of Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ.&lt;SEP&gt;The official JZ is the assigned judge presiding over the matters of Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ.&lt;SEP&gt;JZ is the judicial official assigned to the oversight and proceedings of Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ.&lt;SEP&gt;The initials JZ identify the presiding official assigned to oversee Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ.&lt;SEP&gt;JZ is the designated judge responsible for Case 3:22-cv-01342-JZ.</data>
