  <data key="d7">6.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Michael Wagner expressed disapproval of Fire Star and believed that the Witness's relationship with the company stripped control from him.&lt;SEP&gt;Michael Wagner was involved with Fire Star and claimed to have spoken with them after the witness stopped acting as a go-between.&lt;SEP&gt;Michael Wagner attempted to communicate with Fire Star but was not receiving responses from them.&lt;SEP&gt;Michael Wagner authored an email congratulating the witness on leveraging connections at Fire Star to obtain coal.&lt;SEP&gt;Michael Wagner allegedly instructed Fire Star to stop delivering coal due to quality issues.&lt;SEP&gt;Michael Wagner held telephone conversations regarding matters that concerned Fire Star's records or security.</data>
