  <data key="d7">77.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ, Veritext Legal Solutions) identifies a professional partnership in which Veritext Legal Solutions serves as the primary provider of comprehensive court reporting, transcription, and documentation services for the legal proceedings associated with Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ. As the designated service provider for this litigation, Veritext Legal Solutions is responsible for the professional capture of the legal record, the reporting of depositions, and the generation of official legal transcripts.

Beyond fundamental transcription, Veritext Legal Solutions provides specialized litigation support and administrative services. These responsibilities include the creation of detailed indices for legal records and the systematic organization of documentation associated with court filings. The organization’s involvement ensures that all proceedings related to Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ are accurately documented and organized through their specialized reporting and recording systems.

Veritext Legal Solutions further supports the legal matter by providing document hosting and general record-keeping services. By utilizing their document management systems, the organization ensures that the official transcripts and all related legal documentation are maintained, preserved, and made accessible within the judicial record. Their role is central to the production, indexing, and maintenance of the official transcript and the broader legal record for Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ.</data>
