<edge source="Veritext Legal Solutions" target="Veritext.com">
  <data key="d7">27.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between Veritext Legal Solutions and Veritext.com is defined by the organization’s ownership and management of the domain as its primary digital presence and official website. Veritext.com serves as the central online platform and portal for Veritext Legal Solutions, acting as the official web address through which the company conducts its business activities, shares information with the public, and provides access to its various professional legal services.

Veritext Legal Solutions utilizes Veritext.com to facilitate the delivery of its legal solutions and to provide a vital contact point for its clients and stakeholders. The website is maintained for diverse business purposes, including offering detailed service information and streamlining communication between the organization and those it serves. By operating this digital environment, Veritext Legal Solutions ensures a cohesive and professional online infrastructure that supports its daily operational requirements and informational services.

In addition to its role as a general service portal, Veritext.com is the designated resource for inquiries regarding the company's confidentiality and security practices. As the primary digital domain for the organization, it functions as the authoritative online platform for both the dissemination of professional legal information and the execution of the company’s digital business strategy.</data>
