<edge source="Veritext Legal Solutions" target="Deposition">
  <data key="d7">15.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between a Deposition and Veritext Legal Solutions is characterized by the comprehensive administrative, reporting, and transcription framework provided by the latter. Veritext Legal Solutions serves as the primary entity responsible for the professional recording and documentation of deposition proceedings, ensuring that official transcripts are accurately produced and maintained. Its role encompasses the provision of reporting services required to document the official record of the event, as well as professional transcription and documentation services.

Veritext Legal Solutions also provides the technological platform and administrative support necessary for the deposition event. This includes transcript indexing and the systematic processing of deposition transcripts and exhibits provided by court reporters according to established production standards. By facilitating the recording, transcription, and exhibit management, Veritext Legal Solutions manages the entire documentation lifecycle of the deposition proceeding.</data>
