  <data key="d8">The relation (Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ, Doc #: 71-1) identifies a specific formal filing that constitutes an official component of the legal records associated with Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ. This document is a recognized part of the official court record, having been submitted to the court under the case's unique identifier to serve as a specific piece of documentation within the broader litigation process.

As an official filing, Doc #: 71-1 may function as either an evidentiary or procedural document necessary for the legal proceedings of Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ. It represents a distinct element of the case's comprehensive legal history, ensuring that its contents are integrated into the authoritative record maintained for the judicial matter at hand.</data>
