<edge source="Albion" target="The Witness">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Witness supplied the Albion plant with coal in 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The witness produces 100 percent of the coal used by the Albion plant and delivers it in powder form.&lt;SEP&gt;The Witness intended to use coal deliveries to support the Albion facility.&lt;SEP&gt;The Witness was responsible for monitoring and documenting potential coal supply issues at the Albion plant.</data>
