  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Albion" target="Archbold">
  <data key="d7">8.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between Albion and Archbold is defined by a comprehensive coal supply agreement in which Archbold serves as the sole supplier for the Albion plant. Within this arrangement, Archbold is responsible for grinding coal into a powder format specifically to satisfy the requirements of the Albion facility. This service is provided on an absolutely regular and consistent basis, ensuring that the Albion plant is perpetually serviced to maintain its operations.

Both the Albion and Archbold plants share similar operational scales, with each maintaining coal processing requirements of approximately 35 tons per day. Because Archbold manages the coverage and specific needs of the Albion facility, their logistical and reporting processes are closely integrated. Consequently, the coal usage figures reported by Archbold include the specific amounts attributed to the Albion plant’s consumption.</data>
  <data key="d9">coal distribution,consistent service,facility integration,grinding,industrial operations,industrial processing,industrial service,material processing,ownership,production volume,regular basis,resource distribution,supply,supply chain,supply relationship,usage reporting</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-72864d43546b0fdb0889bb6341c0c099&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00c571593b1228b7b76059ab51abd6c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1acc0c2748bf5b184c2f1284638c9089&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbd2c15dff71dc080694d39bcb9aee57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a84012ee527927df3cba96bd82645063&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0fac00b24251700d101d62ba241bf375&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76b142c69bd1fd0042f02d144521dea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce0536f5d7fd6c2825c2025e7a85ff94</data>
