<edge source="Dwayne" target="Fire Star">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between Dwayne and Fire Star is characterized by Dwayne’s role as a primary representative and central point of contact for the entity. He serves as the functional link through which external parties, including the company Archbold and various witnesses, communicate their logistical and operational requirements. In this capacity, Dwayne is responsible for managing professional relationships, overseeing business matters, and handling account payments on behalf of Fire Star.

Dwayne possesses significant operational authority within Fire Star, maintaining the power to either approve or shut down coal sales and deliveries. He is the individual responsible for managing and adjusting the volume of coal orders, acting as the primary conduit for increasing supply as needed by business partners. Additionally, Dwayne is noted as the representative of Fire Star during the period when ACC intended to terminate its business relationship with the organization, further underscoring his prominent position in the entity's external and commercial affairs.&lt;SEP&gt;Dwayne represents Fire Star in business operations, responding to inquiries about coal shipments and fuel costs.</data>
  <data key="d9">affiliation,business affiliation,communication,control,employment,management,order management,point of contact,professional association,professional representation,professional role,representation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3aa6b92318a7dbc503df2e6bc0457f59&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72864d43546b0fdb0889bb6341c0c099&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5615da5f26bf1a4c451ff93c5d9cf990&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa66b57078d2cf7712dd3f3924568ac6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea56e06fa48990cb993a7e9f44e99a73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbd2c15dff71dc080694d39bcb9aee57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77f207fa8c71ca071a396427e788ad46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-759f6d7d103fee2c466f82f605e71182</data>
  <data key="d11">Deposition by Defendant -- Neil Miller (Manager at Plaintiff) -- April 14, 2023, 1316.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;Deposition by Plaintiff -- Dwayne Jones (Owner of Defendant) -- August 17, 2023, 1101.pdf</data>
  <data key="d12">1777297256</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
