  <data key="d8">Cotton acts as a secondary contact person for coal supply matters when Dwayne is unreachable.&lt;SEP&gt;Dwayne and Cotton are both points of contact for the Deponent regarding coal supply and delivery matters.&lt;SEP&gt;Cotton is described as Dwayne's right-hand man and acts as a truck owner facilitating Dwayne's coal business.&lt;SEP&gt;Cotton is identified as Dwayne's right-hand man.</data>
