<edge source="Dwayne" target="The Witness">
  <data key="d7">7.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The witness contacts Dwayne to adjust coal order volumes in response to mechanical failures or volume forecasts.&lt;SEP&gt;The Witness continued to communicate with Dwayne despite being ordered by Michael Wagner to stop.&lt;SEP&gt;The witness stopped talking to Dwayne in March 2022 following the specific phone call and email events.&lt;SEP&gt;The witness stopped communicating with Dwayne in March 2022 to avoid being caught in the middle of their bosses' dealings with Fire Star.&lt;SEP&gt;Dwayne informed the Witness that Dwayne's trucks could not be used, but stated that the Witness's actions regarding the Witness's own coal were the Witness's own business.&lt;SEP&gt;The Witness attempted to reach Dwayne, the person in control of Fire Star's coal, before reaching out to Cotton.&lt;SEP&gt;Dwayne gave the witness permission to manage coal shipments independently, provided the witness arranged their own transportation.</data>
  <data key="d9">attempted contact,business relationship,ceased communication,communication,conflict avoidance,legal testimony,non-compliance,operational dispute,permission,procurement coordination,professional communication,professional interaction</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3e53329a256cc082bedeaabb7ee866bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b14692172e18d355177e1f52adca6616&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-239b957363afa06896c850b0b3096cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5615da5f26bf1a4c451ff93c5d9cf990&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1acc0c2748bf5b184c2f1284638c9089&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbd2c15dff71dc080694d39bcb9aee57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77f207fa8c71ca071a396427e788ad46</data>
