<edge source="Fire Star" target="Tim">
  <data key="d7">8.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between Fire Star and Tim is defined by Tim’s central role in the company’s administrative and financial operations. As an employee of Fire Star, Tim is responsible for managing all billing, paperwork, and general financial aspects of the organization. The company relies on him to maintain and track critical financial data, specifically concerning the profitability of sales to various customers.

In addition to his financial duties, Tim is tasked with monitoring Fire Star’s official email account and utilizes the organization’s email address for professional correspondence. He serves as the primary point of contact for verifying the receipt of specific communications; for instance, Dwayne Jones directs inquiries to Tim regarding whether Fire Star has received letters from entities such as B&amp;W Resources, Inc.

Tim’s responsibilities also extend to representing Fire Star in matters of business practices and responding to external requests for information, including weight data. Furthermore, he is closely associated with Dwayne Jones and has been instrumental in the company’s response to operational issues, such as instances of nonpayment. His comprehensive management of the company's records makes him the authoritative figure for any questions regarding Fire Star’s internal documentation and correspondence history.</data>
