<edge source="Fire Star" target="Chavies Mine">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Fire Star attempted to procure coal from the Chavies mine, although the mine prioritized customers with existing contracts and only supplied Fire Star when excess capacity was available.&lt;SEP&gt;Fire Star specifically requested and purchased coal produced at the Chavies mine prior to the cessation of requests in 2022.&lt;SEP&gt;Fire Star was unable to get coal from the Chavies Mine because the mine had to prioritize fulfilling obligations to long-term contracted customers after the flood.</data>
