<edge source="Coal" target="The Witness">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Witness managed the grinding and delivery of coal to multiple industrial locations.&lt;SEP&gt;The witness was responsible for coal procurement until March 2022, after which they sought to avoid involvement in the process.&lt;SEP&gt;The Witness requests, grounds, and distributes coal to various industrial facilities.&lt;SEP&gt;The witness claims authority over the coal and manages the specifics of its processing and destination.</data>
  <data key="d9">commodity management,handling,logistics,procurement,professional responsibility,supply,supply chain</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-239b957363afa06896c850b0b3096cab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-106b16a32678dd2303338174088c2dfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77f207fa8c71ca071a396427e788ad46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-890fa85548914bc59a26974a429c4e21</data>
  <data key="d11">Deposition by Defendant -- Neil Miller (Manager at Plaintiff) -- April 14, 2023, 1316.pdf</data>
  <data key="d12">1777295705</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Coal" target="Archbold">
  <data key="d7">7.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Archbold processes raw coal by grinding it into a powder form for industrial use.&lt;SEP&gt;Archbold utilizes its mill to grind and process coal for its own needs and for distribution to other plants.&lt;SEP&gt;Coal was ground at the Archbold facility prior to its delivery to the Belvidere plant.&lt;SEP&gt;Coal is shipped to Archbold where it is ground up and processed at a plant.&lt;SEP&gt;The Archbold plant grinds coal for its own products as well as for other plants.&lt;SEP&gt;Archbold is a specific location where coal status is monitored and reported.&lt;SEP&gt;Coal is the material required to be delivered to the Archbold location under the terms of a contract.</data>
  <data key="d9">delivery,delivery location,industrial processing,inventory management,logistics,manufacturing,material processing,material transformation,milling,processing,production</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-20985475deeff0feffae4d18b011ee8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00c571593b1228b7b76059ab51abd6c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-106b16a32678dd2303338174088c2dfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbd2c15dff71dc080694d39bcb9aee57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff8ea4fb9a276eb3036f6b13650d835&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a2fa8d820719e1257925db86c0ebc64b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d51b6e760a730f18b43bfd8a8366573</data>
  <data key="d11">Deposition by Defendant -- Neil Miller (Manager at Plaintiff) -- April 14, 2023, 1316.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;Deposition by Defendant -- Aric Wentz (Supervisor at Plaintiff) -- April 14, 2023, 0859.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;Deposition by Plaintiff -- Timothy Jones (Owner of Defendant) -- July 17, 2023, 0938.pdf</data>
  <data key="d12">1777299159</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Coal" target="Aluminum Shed">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Coal is stored in aluminum sheds, which have a total combined capacity of 1,600 tons.</data>
  <data key="d9">containment,storage</data>
