<edge source="Ms. Rathke" target="The Witness">
  <data key="d7">41.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between Ms. Rathke and The Witness is characterized by two distinct legal dynamics as presented in the provided records: one of protective legal representation and another of direct examination. Depending on the specific legal proceeding or context, Ms. Rathke acts either as the counsel defending The Witness or as the attorney conducting the formal questioning of The Witness.

In the capacity of legal representative, Ms. Rathke serves as counsel for The Witness during depositions or formal testimony. Her primary function in this role is to provide legal guidance and procedural instructions to ensure the testimony adheres to legal standards while protecting the Witness's interests. She actively monitors the proceedings and intervenes by interjecting with formal legal objections to questions posed by other individuals, such as Mr. Hunter. These objections often target the form and foundation of the questioning to manage the scope of the deposition and prevent the disclosure of privileged communications. Ms. Rathke also handles administrative flow, offering guidance on the presentation of exhibits and ensuring the Witness responds based on personal knowledge rather than speculation, particularly concerning specialized subjects like coal volume requirements.

In a separate context, Ms. Rathke functions as the questioning attorney who conducts the formal examination of The Witness during legal proceedings. In this role, she is responsible for gathering information and building a record regarding business operations and legal claims. Her questioning covers a broad range of topics, including the Witness's professional time, hours worked at Fire Star, and various other business endeavors. She presents documents and exhibits to the Witness for identification and probes their knowledge of past events, contractual compliance, and coal supply agreements. Furthermore, Ms. Rathke examines the accuracy and truthfulness of the Witness’s interrogatory answers, ensuring that all testimony regarding business communications and dealings is thoroughly vetted for the legal record.</data>
  <data key="d9">Legal Representation,Objection,advocacy,defense,deposition,examination,guidance,inquiry,instruction,interjection,interrogation,legal counsel,legal defense,legal examination,legal procedure,legal proceeding,legal questioning,legal representation,objection,procedural interjection,questioning,representation,testimony,testimony clarification</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b14692172e18d355177e1f52adca6616&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5615da5f26bf1a4c451ff93c5d9cf990&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1acc0c2748bf5b184c2f1284638c9089&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-106b16a32678dd2303338174088c2dfa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3cf9a12f8ab261dacc4fe581a64518c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77f207fa8c71ca071a396427e788ad46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d6d709d0ec6b3472961b88797a09fc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-890fa85548914bc59a26974a429c4e21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05cd0ef67a4759a9e91d7bd173221f6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37bd5da834c461a6ccd2a7eb73c0210a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e21ed3795086662478d7a51f321f88e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6a6e5d2f4c03b33472c4185b1291af6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a2fa8d820719e1257925db86c0ebc64b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c518205befdf2e877ded1419ba356a90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51f8a4880c779327848a6447b6a9410b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8fa155c99076902d5c68d436af59b4c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65ca06b1229dac02f972ebae8fde3f98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0fdeef1a7af602b992743ca983179b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa96ecbf448943278b52e872cc3984a4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bf5b8711461b0e50ae4d1999bbc86ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b68abd5df047acac26c37b8f51c0f65b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc791897e9c35dc37b1a1c68ac95a4d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c897eacbc52ea3409f410ddbf1dd519&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9849773656bd11ce4107626d03972b64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-872baedd657194f10bff17517ac33313&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad5c79f834b06c6743b856f054cf1d35&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62b1979b82b13aa473c9984e5d068597&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3685a8c4ea16ed81736bdfa10022fc8d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70464475fce6ebfbef39a68f9d9e6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d9e103df6e64a7c9f08b2fe14a11ac4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26133255971de373d8862139ecc99220&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2303ff741d8017a5176d75a2abdfe5ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d41d933f94ead56d3ee9ccb33dd28b07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c49f929503157c8fd745523af065f8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5112ed7e479baa078942ba54c24c9817&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c04f49f2f1828e187e2d46075aba09f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-428d5f444613568ed50ee1bda1193ac8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30d0b22d79b47320c1f6cc47e1d3a998&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41879e062c3be5c70a69159a6ce804a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3768689425a6da71a09b43a110e4c9b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f43f20395a640ee