<edge source="The Witness" target="Deposition">
  <data key="d7">8.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between a Deposition and The Witness defines the latter as the primary individual and central subject responsible for providing sworn testimony during this legal event. Serving as the deponent, the Witness delivers formal oral testimony under oath, which constitutes a critical component of the deposition proceeding.

Throughout the deposition process, the Witness is the primary subject of questioning and is tasked with responding to various inquiries. Their participation is integral to the formal discovery phase of legal proceedings, where their sworn statements are recorded to facilitate the gathering of evidence and the clarification of facts relevant to the matter at hand.</data>
  <data key="d9">Legal Participation,Testimony,formal testimony,legal participation,legal proceeding,participation,sworn testimony,testimony</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ce0536f5d7fd6c2825c2025e7a85ff94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c897eacbc52ea3409f410ddbf1dd519&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9849773656bd11ce4107626d03972b64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d699f913a8b37597b19cd0e1b1798b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70464475fce6ebfbef39a68f9d9e6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-883a650c59e4458dc68f11e575383ce9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26133255971de373d8862139ecc99220&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30d0b22d79b47320c1f6cc47e1d3a998</data>
  <data key="d11">Deposition by Defendant -- Aric Wentz (Supervisor at Plaintiff) -- April 14, 2023, 0859.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;Deposition by Plaintiff -- Dwayne Jones (Owner of Defendant) -- August 17, 2023, 1101.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;Deposition by Plaintiff -- Timothy Jones (Owner of Defendant) -- July 17, 2023, 0938.pdf</data>
  <data key="d12">1777299113</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
