<edge source="The Witness" target="Fire Star Energy">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Witness has been the owner of Fire Star Energy since its inception around 2015.&lt;SEP&gt;The Witness operated the business under the name Fire Star Energy prior to the formation of Fire Star.&lt;SEP&gt;The Witness describes the process of issuing Fire Star Energy's invoices and refers to the company's billing actions as 'our' process.&lt;SEP&gt;The Witness speaks on behalf of Fire Star Energy and describes the company's dual role as a producer and broker of coal.</data>
