<edge source="Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ" target="Deposition">
  <data key="d7">15.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship (Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ, Deposition) characterizes the deposition as a formal and central proceeding within the legal case identified as 3:22-cv-01342-JZ. It serves as a core component of the discovery process, functioning as a primary mechanism for evidence-gathering and the acquisition of recorded testimony. As a formal event, the deposition is integral to the broader legal proceedings and is conducted to ensure that testimony is documented and preserved for the case.

Furthermore, the deposition constitutes a vital part of the official legal record and the documentation filed for Case: 3:22-cv-01342-JZ. It is recognized as a core testimonial component of the case's historical and procedural records. By capturing recorded testimony, the deposition becomes a permanent element of the legal evidence and proceedings, supporting the formal discovery and litigation requirements of the judicial process.</data>
