<edge source="Archbold Plant" target="Troy Plant">
  <data key="d7">6.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Archbold plant regularly grinds coal and sends it to the Troy plant in Indiana.&lt;SEP&gt;The Archbold Plant ground and delivered coal to the Troy plant when a silo failure occurred at the Troy facility.&lt;SEP&gt;The Archbold plant and Troy plant are both part of the same industrial system or supply network.&lt;SEP&gt;The Archbold plant grinds coal for the Troy plant and covers its coal needs.&lt;SEP&gt;The Archbold plant produces ground coal that is regularly supplied to meet the requirements of the Troy plant.&lt;SEP&gt;The Archbold plant provides ground coal product specifically for the operations of the Troy plant.</data>
