<edge source="Archbold Plant" target="Belvidere Plant">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Belvidere Plant is identified as the facility with coal usage most similar to the Archbold Plant.&lt;SEP&gt;The Archbold plant typically grinds coal for the Belvidere plant, acting as a gap filler when the latter lacks quality supply.&lt;SEP&gt;The Archbold Plant provides ground coal to the Belvidere plant when the latter experiences supply or processing issues.&lt;SEP&gt;Coal originally intended for the Archbold Plant was diverted to the Belvidere Plant due to operational inefficiencies at Archbold.&lt;SEP&gt;Coal was delivered directly to the Belvidere Plant from suppliers when the Archbold Plant was unable to grind the material.</data>
  <data key="d9">comparison,facility coordination,grinding services,industrial similarity,logistical diversion,logistics,material transfer,supply chain</data>
